{"lemma":"خُمُّ","slug":"خُمُّ","root":"خ.م.م","root_slug":"خ-م-م","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-م-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11445","n11448","n11449"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8F%D9%85%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become stinking, to get rotten, to acquire a foul smell"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of خَمَّ (ḵamma) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to sweep, to scoop"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of خَمَّ (ḵamma) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"coop for domestic birds to be fattened, pen for poultry, brooding cage, henhouse, pigeon’s home and the like"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"See ق م م (q m m) with this meaning.\n\nFrom Persian خم (xom)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11445","headword_ar":"خَمَّ","root":"xm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, K) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) [the latter irreg.,] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xumuwmN","text_ar":"خُمُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~N","text_ar":"خَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(flesh-meat)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, stinking;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) said of what is roasted, or cooked; (S;) or mostly said of what is cooked, and what is roasted: (IDrd, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became altered for the worse in odour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of roasted meat, and of meat cut into strips and dried: (A'Obeyd, TA:) or"},{"kind":"page_break","n":807},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became stinking after having been thoroughly cooked"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and said also of milk, (JK, K,) in like manner, (JK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it became altered by the bad odour of the skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and corrupt:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axm~","text_ar":"اخمّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, (JK, S, K,) in both cases: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~N","text_ar":"خَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, said of a cake of bread not thoroughly baked, signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"becoming altered in odour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~a","text_ar":"خَمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xumuwmN","text_ar":"خُمُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is likewise said of a man. (TA. [See also 10.]) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa laA yaxim~u","text_ar":"هُوَ لَا يَخِمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He will not become altered"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from his state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from his liberality,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"generosity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa Als~amonu","text_ar":"هُوَ السَّمْنُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yaxim~u","text_ar":"لَا يَخِمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) [lit.] meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It is the clarified butter"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that will not become altered"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the worse"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) a prov., relating to a man when one speaks well of him, and praises him. (S, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa Als~um~u laA yaxim~u","text_ar":"هُوَ السُّمُّ لَا يَخِمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It is unmixed poison."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~N","text_ar":"خَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weeping violently."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yaxim~u","text_ar":"هُوَ يَخِمُّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He weeps violently."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TK.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~a","text_ar":"خَمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~u","text_ar":"خَمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cleaned out"},{"kind":"text","text":"a well: (S, K: *) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he swept"},{"kind":"text","text":"a tent, or house, or chamber: (JK, S, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axtm~","text_ar":"اختمّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, (S, K,) in both cases. (TA, and so in some copies of the K.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yaxum~u viyaAbahu","text_ar":"هُوَ يَخُمُّ ثِيَابَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He eulogizes him, commends him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speaks well of him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~ahu bivanaA='K HasanK","text_ar":"خَمَّهُ بِثَنَا=ءٍ حَسَنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~N","text_ar":"خَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He eulogized him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [and so, app.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~ahu","text_ar":"خَمَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"alone; for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~N","text_ar":"خَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eulogizing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~N","text_ar":"خَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cutting;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AixotimaAmN","text_ar":"اِخْتِمَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~a Aln~aAqapa","text_ar":"خَمَّ النَّاقَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~N","text_ar":"خَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He milked the she-camel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~a","text_ar":"خَمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he turned in his thumb upon his palm when milking."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xum~a","text_ar":"خُمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a domestic fowl,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was confined in a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xum~","text_ar":"خُمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coop."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","S","K","IDrd","TA","TK"]},{"entry_id":"n11448","headword_ar":"خَمٌّ","root":"xm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAm~N","text_ar":"خَامٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AA, S,) applied to flesh-meat (AA, S, K) that is roasted or cooked, (AA, S,) or mostly to what is cooked and what is roasted, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Stinking;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxim~N","text_ar":"مُخِمٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (AA, S:) or this last signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"altered in odour, but not yet corrupt"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, JK, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like a stinking dead body."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","AA","S","Lth","JK","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n11449","headword_ar":"خُمٌّ","root":"xm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coop, for domestic fowls:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, K:) [and so, in modern Arabic,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xun~N","text_ar":"خُنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] thought by ISd to be so called because of its foul smell. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"receptacle made of matting"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of reeds, such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawoSar~ap","text_ar":"قَوْصَرَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which straw is put, for the domestic hen to lay her eggs therein,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to hatch therein."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hollow dug in the ground, in the bottom of which are put ashes, and then new-born lambs or kids are put therein:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ximamapN","text_ar":"خِمَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["ISd","K"]}]}}